title: Openstreetmap, Rheinland-Pfalz Railways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Rheinland-Pfalz Railways, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and shows the locations of the Railway infrastructure in the  administrative area Rheinland-Pfalz in the country of Germany. Railways include trams, subways, and standard trains. This railway data set was uploaded as a poly line shape file and includes attribute information for Feature name and feature type.
